Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.95,0:01:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要打倒的是明治政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.75,0:01:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後建立真正四民平等的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.95,0:01:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此而已，再見了，傻瓜蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.35,0:01:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下!王八蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.79,0:01:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這種王八蛋\N我可不會讓你一個人去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.99,0:01:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.13,0:01:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的朋友雖然重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.59,0:01:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，和以前的朋友比起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.63,0:01:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不得不捨棄現在的所有……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.63,0:01:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十四話半夜之戰！\N左之助再一次VS劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.74,0:02:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宴會？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.07,0:02:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.97,0:02:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想，偶而大家熱鬧一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.31,0:02:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心，你說呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.81,0:02:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！那真好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.38,0:02:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.92,0:02:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我當然沒有異議，不過….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.15,0:02:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說要熱鬧一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.86,0:02:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裏有那麼多錢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.42,0:02:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便說說是不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.29,0:02:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.93,0:02:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之你說呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.93,0:02:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.23,0:02:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是錢的話，我有辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.13,0:02:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.43,0:02:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎左之助！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.84,0:02:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是不是想靠我呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，不行的….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.21,0:02:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠我去教人練劍的這點收入\N供應你們這些食客吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.31,0:02:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經沒有餘力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.41,0:02:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可沒有多餘的錢喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.05,0:02:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說不行，就絕對不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.08,0:02:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別那麼緊張嘛，大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.65,0:02:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心錢的事，看我的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.76,0:02:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你雖然這麼說….\N又要紅著臉去欠帳了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.06,0:03:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對妙小姐不好意思的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.56,0:03:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是，我們在這裏辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.40,0:03:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我家？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.10,0:03:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，若在這裏，不怕被打擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.64,0:03:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有自家人，可以好好樂一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.57,0:03:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是這樣，我是無所謂….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.14,0:03:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，就這麼說定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.38,0:03:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大小姐，替我邀小惠一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.85,0:03:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找惠小姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛，我和他是死對頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.29,0:03:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熱鬧一點比較好嘛，拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.89,0:03:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿，這種怪事也有\N左之助竟會邀起小惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.09,0:03:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩個老是吵架的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.63,0:03:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪了！\N今天的左之助太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.63,0:03:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助是不是哪裏有病啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.20,0:03:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了，左之助這傢伙\N一定是赤報隊的嫌疑洗清太高興了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.64,0:03:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此！所以請客啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.15,0:03:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是這樣的話今天晚上\N嘿！嘿！大家大鬧一場吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.78,0:03:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好熱鬧一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤報隊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.40,0:04:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.40,0:04:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，阿克！你在正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.03,0:04:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的，可不可以借點錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.61,0:04:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦！整個錢包啊\N走紅的畫師果然不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你要用的話，要趁早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.98,0:04:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚決定襲擊內務省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.65,0:04:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚是新月，夜色昏暗\N正是摸黑的好時機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.69,0:04:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內務省可以說是明治政府的中樞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.19,0:04:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先讓這裏的機能完全停止\N然後，各省府一處接一處.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.30,0:04:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚是嗎？….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.74,0:04:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了左之？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼，我在想，這樣正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.91,0:04:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那這錢我先借走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.51,0:04:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.28,0:05:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真豐盛啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧！大家也都等得餓了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.02,0:05:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來幫忙，來幫忙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.39,0:05:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小雀，別急得摔交喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們別鬧的太過火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.97,0:05:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以添麻煩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.80,0:05:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，可以開動了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.07,0:05:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是\N讓左之助請總覺得怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.91,0:05:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這錢\N可不是做壞事弄來的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.88,0:05:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不願意替你分罪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.22,0:05:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這彆扭的個性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.95,0:05:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可真是一輩子也改不了啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.02,0:05:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嘛，彼此彼此！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.76,0:05:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是說左之助和小惠\N兩個人是同類嘍！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.06,0:05:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！兩個一對，真配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.07,0:05:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了！左之助和惠小姐\N難得的慶祝酒席嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.37,0:06:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊！來吧，喝到爛醉為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.28,0:06:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喝吧！熱鬧一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.81,0:06:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這老傢伙都準備好了啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.78,0:06:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心，我幫你倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.75,0:06:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,承蒙薰小姐動手啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.09,0:06:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰小姐連倒酒的方法都不懂啊\N真差勁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.36,0:06:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我教你，讓我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.76,0:06:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，我先的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.09,0:06:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大小姐就躲一邊吧！\N來，劍心，請喝一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.33,0:06:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是惠小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.07,0:06:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說什麼「不愧是惠小姐」啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.34,0:06:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再也不替你倒酒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥，你也喝一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.42,0:06:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.85,0:06:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還只是個小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.42,0:06:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把我當小鬼看待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.39,0:06:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我乃明神禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.09,0:06:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喝一兩升酒，不算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.96,0:06:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好看著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.81,0:07:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.05,0:07:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如大小姐所言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.61,0:07:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃才是你的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.95,0:07:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍先生，請給我返杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請，請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.36,0:07:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真，真難以置信\N竟用同一個杯子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.99,0:07:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！好喝！….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.60,0:07:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,髒，你們這些大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.83,0:07:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不服氣的話，就趕快變大人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.54,0:07:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？你說什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.47,0:07:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠，我也想請你倒酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.51,0:07:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快叫醫生來….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.08,0:07:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然如此，我也喝了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.28,0:07:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰，薰小姐，亂喝是不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.29,0:07:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可，可是….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.86,0:07:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是她自己說別管的嘛\N你就別理她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.09,0:08:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，劍先生炸豆腐如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.64,0:08:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.87,0:08:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.37,0:08:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.71,0:08:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終究，我是個連倒酒都不會的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.35,0:08:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,料理也差勁，又沒女人味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.22,0:08:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了劍術，毫無優點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.89,0:08:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個滿身汗臭味的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.89,0:08:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你，不可以這樣\N看低你自己啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.39,0:08:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這女孩喝醉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.96,0:08:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰小姐一喝醉就變得愛纏人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.46,0:08:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，可是呀\N我有一項不輸任何人的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.20,0:08:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那，那就是….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.51,0:08:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是….哈….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.28,0:08:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭！自己不好意思說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.45,0:08:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是，變得愛笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.18,0:08:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，可是….怎麼辦好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.09,0:08:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說嘍！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.95,0:09:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶，大小姐\N今天就不用拘禮，說了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.42,0:09:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之，你饒了我吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.09,0:09:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！劍心\N你有在聽我說話嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.46,0:09:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酒好臭！你離劍心遠一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.77,0:09:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你敢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.47,0:09:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩位住手，我受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.88,0:09:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心，一對一勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.36,0:09:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喝不下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.09,0:09:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真差勁，劍心！\N豁出去了！放開點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.95,0:10:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該走了….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.07,0:10:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後的晚餐….\N放開心情享受了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.24,0:10:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受這麼多照顧，算是一點報答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.04,0:10:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的可以嗎？左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.95,0:10:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把現在給拋棄也….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.61,0:10:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白癡，我個性可就這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.45,0:10:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我自己決定的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.92,0:10:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不分什麼過去和現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.42,0:10:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嘛….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.46,0:10:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在現在選了赤報隊\N我由衷地感謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.80,0:10:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走吧，否則到內務省天都亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.24,0:10:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起了，各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.01,0:10:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不敢希望你們能諒解我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.51,0:11:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我來說\N到底赤報隊是特別的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.35,0:11:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能遇到你們真好，來生再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.08,0:11:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時候，大家剖心相待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.52,0:11:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翻天覆地大鬧一場吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.26,0:11:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.29,0:11:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏乃是掌管警察\N和地方行政的重要地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.62,0:11:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內務省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.85,0:12:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時候到了….走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.09,0:12:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎，怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.95,0:12:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸彈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,襲擊呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.02,0:12:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連發的….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.09,0:12:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯人還潛伏在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.09,0:12:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,負責警備的人全部到大門集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.56,0:12:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你調整導火線的長度\N以控制爆炸的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.83,0:12:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想的周到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.77,0:12:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能入侵屋內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.07,0:12:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以說等於是成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.47,0:12:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內務省將化為粉末\N那些警察也一起….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.41,0:12:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趕回來為止，將決定成敗\N一口氣衝過庭院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.14,0:12:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別停！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.33,0:13:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.40,0:13:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之，這個人是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.77,0:13:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.50,0:13:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說中的斬人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.67,0:13:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？那位傳言中\N有名的斬人拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.18,0:13:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,維新志士又到我們面前\N想阻擋我們了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.78,0:13:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過這一次我們赤報隊會贏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.19,0:13:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是炸裂彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.55,0:13:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！使用這個首先是內務省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.72,0:13:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後接連地炸掉東京裏的各省廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.32,0:13:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以打倒明治政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.99,0:13:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若有人想要阻礙\N即使是斬人者拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.96,0:13:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也格殺勿論！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.64,0:13:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這….怎麼可能！為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.68,0:13:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍速之快把導火線週遭弄成真空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.02,0:13:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的劍術也只有\N劍心才做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.35,0:13:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋！你這維新志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.79,0:14:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒用的阿克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.32,0:14:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是他的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.03,0:14:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這傢伙是政府的走狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.16,0:14:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心也和我一樣\N認為現在的政府並不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.77,0:14:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，身為建立現在政府之一份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.04,0:14:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他比我們感痛更深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.27,0:14:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之，你幹嘛替他說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.71,0:14:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我第一次和劍心決鬥時\N也和你現在一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.61,0:14:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，被打的一敗塗地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.25,0:14:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這奇妙的緣份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.65,0:14:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把他當成朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.25,0:14:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過\N從現在起我選擇了赤報隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經不能再回頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.86,0:14:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心，如果無論如何\N你都要阻礙我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.03,0:14:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是你，我也不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.43,0:14:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之，這是你身為一個男人所選的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.97,0:14:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也沒資格說你什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.44,0:14:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我所要做的事\N只是要阻止你們的兇行罷了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.24,0:14:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心了，劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等，等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.38,0:15:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之！\N你怎可空手對付拔刀齊….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.69,0:15:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了劍心！\N為什麼不反過來拔刀呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.66,0:15:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.76,0:15:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之，我不會和你客氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.67,0:15:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也希望你這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.81,0:15:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是龍槌閃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.91,0:15:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.22,0:15:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡，竟敢把左之….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.86,0:15:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了！\N這是短導火線的炸裂彈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.23,0:15:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你出招前就已爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.27,0:15:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不見了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.50,0:15:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就憑這樣是打不倒劍心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.91,0:16:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月岡，看來你若使用炸裂彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.91,0:16:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連累一般庶民\N造成大量無辜犧牲是必然的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.55,0:16:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此骯髒的作法\N沒有理由原諒你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.02,0:16:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說什麼乾淨骯髒的\N為達成目的不擇手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.26,0:16:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能為赤報隊\N和隊長洗清污名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.47,0:16:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這維新志士是不懂的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.60,0:16:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就因為我是維新志士\N更無法坐視你們的愚行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要用斬人者的態度和我說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.91,0:16:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿克！住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.92,0:16:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心你的對手是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.96,0:16:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿克！劍心交給我，你快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.76,0:16:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察來之前，盡快解決了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.76,0:16:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.37,0:17:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.61,0:17:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.75,0:17:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊克！趁現在，快去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.49,0:17:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明知事情會如此\N還願為赤報隊友人月岡捨命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.79,0:17:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊克！你在幹嘛！還不快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.46,0:17:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋！我能丟下你不管嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.60,0:17:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手左之！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.97,0:17:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別再打了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.34,0:17:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會被拔刀齊給殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.31,0:17:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之！會死的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.96,0:17:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.30,0:18:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之….   對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.81,0:18:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你，替左之助療傷好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.32,0:18:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事吧左之！\N竟把左之弄成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.06,0:18:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別以為這樣就算贏了！\N我還有很多炸裂彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.19,0:18:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等左之回復後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.70,0:18:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次找機會一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.30,0:18:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.97,0:18:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你剛才說，我的所為是愚行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.44,0:18:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你不也是明治維新的斬人者嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.91,0:18:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和明治政府一樣是偽善者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.99,0:19:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還在笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.69,0:19:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼，被叫為偽善者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.53,0:19:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不但不否認反而一笑置之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.87,0:19:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.07,0:19:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之！現在馬上幫你療傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.00,0:19:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心….謝了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.44,0:19:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣，可以不用成為\N真正的假官軍就了事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.45,0:19:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.03,0:19:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還只是個不成熟的小鬼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.00,0:19:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相樂隊長….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.59,0:20:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛….又輸給劍心那小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.85,0:20:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊克！你在那裏啊克！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.86,0:20:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧啊克，一個人又….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.87,0:20:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之！怎麼了那傷？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.21,0:20:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩，是不是喝醉酒\N腳踩到水溝摔倒了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.98,0:20:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的，你這傻蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.61,0:20:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了，你才真的酒癖差呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.65,0:20:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍先生，這傷是刀背所造….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，是出了一些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.02,0:20:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可沒喝得那樣，討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.50,0:20:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那件事之後\N月岡津南在做些什麼？
